    "plain_content":  "Thanks for signing up. We think you\u0027ll love it here.\n\nAmore is more than a dating app. It\u0027s a place to find love. Join the 200,000 people who have already connected with the right person.\n\nSuccess Stories\n\nMeet Our Newest Members In Your Area\n\nAlison T.\nLos Angeles\n\nDave P.\nMalibu\n\nFrequently Asked Questions\n\nHow does it all work?\n\nYou complete our 100-point profile questionnaire so we can get to know you and what you\u0027re looking for in a partner. Then the old matchmaker goes to work. Our algorithm will pair you with carefully vetted potential matches every day. If you\u0027re both interested, you can start to get to know each other.\n\nHow many matches do I get in a day?\n\nYou get 3 matches every day with the free plan. If you *upgrade to our premium offering* ( http:// ) , you will see 6 matches a day.\n\nHow are my matches selected?\n\nThe answers you provide to our profile questionnaire and our matchmaking algorithm pair you up with people who align your personality, lifestyle, interests, relationship values, and more! And our machine learning model gets smarter every time you match so we can refine your personal recommendations each day.\n\nRead More FAQs\n\nInstagram ( http:// )\n\nTwitter ( http:// )\n\nSupport ( http:// )\n\nBlog ( http:// )\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://sendgrid.com/ )",
